Hi everyone! 

For those of you who are new followers or clients of mine, I’m Dani. Master Stylist / Master Colorist @ghstudiosofficial_

I am feeling extremely grateful and blessed to have found my calling so early on in my life. I have been interested in all things beauty since I was a child and for as long as I can remember. It feels like this is exactly what I was always meant to do. Now, I have been doing hair professionally for 7+ years. 

Although I am all the way obsessed with creating and the art of hair period, my TRUE passion is making others feel like the best versions of themselves. That has to be one of the most gratifying feelings in the world to me. My heart has been poured out into my work since day one. I am honestly over the moon that I get to do what I love day in and day out and that I get to call this my “job”. 

This is such an incredible and beautiful career. I am never not learning. So many opportunities and people have come into my life because of it. I feel extremely lucky to say the least. This is your sign to chase your dreams! I could not be happier that I took the leap and decided to pursue this career.

To all of my existing clients and now friends: Thank you so much for trusting me! I am eternally grateful for all of the connections we’ve made as they keep me motivated to work harder and stay inspired. 

I cannot wait to see what the future has in store! 
This is only the beginning. 🖤🤍
